{"tid":2161831,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"朗豪坊Black Magic","createTime":"2020-08-17T19:10:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-20T10:22:37.000Z","uid":317505,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"74a9dceccace389b85ffcdce80b8f04058b2bbde","tid":2161831,"uid":317505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T19:10:47.000Z","msg":"某日放工想搵地方坐低閒hea<br />\n但又冇得堂食<br />\n就去咗朗豪坊駁去cordis 條天橋打算坐下<br />\n<br />\n天橋兩邊有啲坐位（其實又唔係坐位，有貼signage 唔可以坐，不過佢又設計成極誘人嘅坐位咁，見到就會明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n雖然有寫話唔可以坐，但又見到有男女老幼兩小無猜等等喺度食嘢啊吹水啊睇報紙咁，咁我又開心加入坐低睇下連登咁<br />\n<br />\n點知打開個連登app都未㩒到去熱門，有個保安哥哥就用奔跑模式衝咗埋嚟好客氣又chok晒聲咁：<br />\n<br />\n「唔好意思，呢度係酒店範圍唔可以坐㗎」<br />\n<br />\n我即刻企番起身企到直一直，仲有啲慾望同盡責嘅保安哥哥salute! 同時又滿頭問題點解佢淨係捉我........ 唔通我......<br />\n<br />\n於是我企咗喺度觀察咗10分鐘，發現保安哥哥對於坐喺度嘅人，真係有啲捉，有啲唔捉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> &mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n我決定，一定要破解呢個朗豪坊 Black Magic <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n以下係無俾捉嘅識玩街坊：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3HQB445.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3HQB445.png&h=ee08c7a7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RSr9FDv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRSr9FDv.png&h=bbb53f40&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LGGNsiB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLGGNsiB.png&h=c552ed8b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HVFngb0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHVFngb0.png&h=ea33f7d5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"75b96d9c64857ebab878c022691edfdf00a6093f","tid":2161831,"uid":165355,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T20:17:56.000Z","msg":"保安專捉樣衰柒頭<br />\n<br />\n已破解"},{"pid":"8e2e7d660687e27de88d84152408fdbee63fd0d4","tid":2161831,"uid":123456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score"